name: Worried Man Blues
comments: While the song is credited to A.P. Carter on the record, this is one of many traditional songs that he collected and made known to a wider audience. There are other similar songs with different lyrics; this is believed to be the earliest recording for the version titled "Worried Man Blues". Re-recorded in 1935.
